---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="A few words about the person behind Lotus Meditation."
	pubDate={new Date()}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Hi — I'm <strong>Anh-Tuan Mai</strong>, the volunteer behind Lotus Meditation.
	</p>

	<p>
		By day I work as a software engineer based in Paris. By practice, I'm a
		long-time student of meditation and mindfulness — and Lotus Meditation is the small,
		non-profit space where I share what I've learned alongside a community of friends
		and fellow practitioners.
	</p>

	<p>
		This site is built and maintained on free time, with no ads and no commercial intent.
		Everything you find here will always be free.
	</p>

	<p>
		If you'd like to get involved, contribute, or simply say hello, you'll find
		contact details once the site moves out of construction. Thanks for stopping by 🙏
	</p>
</Layout>
